    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. i noticed u mentioned \"well-coiffed\" and \"neat\" hair. we have a fairly diverse group of executives, including some women with more natural hair textures like braids or afros. how should they handle their hair to make sure they still fit that \"authoritative\" and \"polished\" look you described? like, are there certain styles they should avoid to stay professional?",
