    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, so u're saying braids can be \"distracting\" or \"attention-seeking\"? thats a bit surprising. what makes a braid less professional than, say, a blowout or a sleek bob? it feels like you're implying that natural styles are inherently less formal or less serious than straight hair styles. can u explain why those specific styles would be seen as a problem in a boardroom?",
